<doc f='codebrowser/d3xp/script/Script_Compiler.cpp' l='1763'>/*
================
idCompiler::ParseForStatement

Form of for statement with a counter:

	a = 0;
start:					&lt;&lt; patch4
	if ( !( a &lt; 10 ) ) {
		goto end;		&lt;&lt; patch1
	} else {
		goto process;	&lt;&lt; patch3
	}

increment:				&lt;&lt; patch2
	a = a + 1;
	goto start;			&lt;&lt; goto patch4

process:
	statements;
	goto increment;		&lt;&lt; goto patch2

end:

Form of for statement without a counter:

	a = 0;
start:					&lt;&lt; patch2
	if ( !( a &lt; 10 ) ) {
		goto end;		&lt;&lt; patch1
	}

process:
	statements;
	goto start;			&lt;&lt; goto patch2

end:
================
*/</doc>
